128
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:00,800
But the doctors didn't.

129
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,040
So I suggest you think carefully.

130
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,200
If you continue to deny everything,

131
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,840
in the end, the only one facing legal punishment

132
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,920
will be you alone.

133
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:11,880
I don't understand what you're talking about.

134
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,130
I don't understand.

135
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,290
Let me break it down for you.

136
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:16,520
Ten years ago,

137
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,450
