142
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:25,940
You've hated him for 10 years.

143
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:27,760
You got angrier and angrier,

144
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,480
so you returned to Dongzhou.

145
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:32,040
You were determined to destroy their marriage.

146
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:34,280
You couldn't stand that they had a child together.

147
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,400
So you took advantage of Pei Xi

148
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,720
