149
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:39,780
You manipulated Pei Xinlu into killing his own son.

150
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,720
You even fantasized about rekindling your relationship with him.

151
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,720
Then giving him a healthy child,

152
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:44,720
