163
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,720
If it weren't for her,

164
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,800
you could have stayed with Pei Xinlu,

165
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,560
and avoided these ten painful years.

166
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,560
So you interfered in someone else's marriage.

167
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,760
I didn't interfere.

168
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,240
Zhou Wanrou was the mistress.

169
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,160
So you killed her.

170
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:11,280
I didn't mean to kill her.

171
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:12,680
I only hurt her.

172
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:27,480
Back then, Pei Xinlu

173
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:30,010
wanted to expand the company's new business.

174
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,280
Behind your back,

175
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:33,610
