176
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:37,120
You couldn't bear the betrayal.

177
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,560
That's why you hated her so much

178
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:40,480
that you wanted to get revenge on Zhou Wanrou.

179
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,520
That's not all.

180
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:43,760
Ten years ago.

181
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:46,280
He and Zhou Wanrou killed my child.

182
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,400
I can never be a mother again.

183
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,560
What else?

184
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:53,810
Just say it here.

185
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:56,050
When did you get together with her?

186
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,320
Say something.

187
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,970
Did you break up with me because of her?

188
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,600
Can she give you resources?

189
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,960
