218
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,600
And then

219
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,520
Peixi was born.

220
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:57,560
So you manipulated Pei Xinlu into killing Peixi.

221
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:59,640
You wanted to take revenge on Zhou Wanrou,

222
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:02,120
to make her feel the pain of losing a child.

223
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,360
I'm right, aren't I?

224
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,640
That's right.

225
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:08,480
I witnessed Pei Xi's accidental fall.

226
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,280
Don't kill me.

227
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:10,520
Dad.

228
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,320
Xixi.

229
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,280
But I still told Zhou Wanrou

230
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:17,280
that I ordered Pei Xinlu to push her son down.

231
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:18,960
Because only this way,

232
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,560
could she truly understand

233
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:22,240
the pain of losing a child.

234
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,720
Only then could she feel what I felt.

235
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,260
Not enough, right?

236
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:28,610
Just Pei Xi alone isn't enough.

237
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:31,240
The person you truly resent is Zhou Wanrou.

238
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,440
If you don't kill her,

239
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,850
you definitely won't stop.

240
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:39,600
Killing Pei Xi

241
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:42,960
has made you addicted to murder, hasn't it?

242
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:45,560
Then you quickly killed Zhou Wanrou.

243
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,600
She came looking for me herself.

244
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:50,000
What do you mean by that text message you sent me?

245
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:52,530
What do you mean Pei Xi was killed by Pei Xinlu?

246
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,280
What?

247
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,520
You don't believe me?

248
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,680
Then let me tell you something else.

249
00:13:58,680 --> 00:14:00,920
I told Pei Xinlu to push Pei Xi down.

250
00:14:00,920 --> 00:14:03,360
I saw him push Pei Xi with my own eyes.

251
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,760
I watched your son get impaled by steel bars.

252
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:06,560
Impossible.

253
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,920
Pei Xi was Pei Xinlu's biological son.

254
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:10,680
How could he possibly kill his own son?

255
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:12,360
He always listens to me.

256
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:15,620
The way he betrayed me to please you back then

257
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:17,800
is exactly how he's come back to me now.

258
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:20,680
If you hadn't taken advantage of the situation,

259
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:22,400
I wouldn't have lost my child.

260
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,640
So Pei Xi is here to pay with his life.

261
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,040
That's nonsense.

262
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:27,960
When I got together with Pei Xinlu,

263
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:30,360
I had no idea you two were already together.

264
00:14:30,520 --> 00:14:31,850
What did Pei Xi do wrong?

265
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:34,680
He was such an innocent, pure child.

266
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,120
I wished I could

267
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:38,160
stay by his side 24 hours a day.

268
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:40,200
I was just hoping he would gradually recover

269
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,730
to be like normal children.

270
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:44,660
I was careless just that one time,

271
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:45,440
just once,

272
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:47,240
and you got him killed.

273
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,840
So you're free now.

274
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,600
You should be thanking me.

275
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:51,600
That stupid son of yours,

276
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:52,640
what's the point of keeping him anyway?

277
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:53,680
Shut up!

278
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:55,530
I want you to pay with your life.

279
00:15:20,160 --> 00:15:22,620
Zhou Wanrou was very emotional at that time.

280
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:25,680
I was afraid she would lose control and hurt me.

281
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:27,560
I was filled with hatred at that moment,

282
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:29,000
so I beat her up.

283
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:31,280
But I panicked afterwards,

284
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,120
so I called Fox.

285
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,600
Her subordinate killed the person.

286
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:51,200
Not me.

287
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:51,880
Fox?

288
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,480
Which fox?

289
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:54,920
The codename is Fox,

290
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:56,240
the animal fox.

291
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,860
Finally getting to the point.

292
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:02,520
Tell me about it.

293
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:03,600
How did you meet?

294
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:06,320
A year ago.

295
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:09,560
I met Fox on a forum

296
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:11,640
where people share emotional experiences.

297
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:13,240
We talked a lot.

298
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:15,160
She made me feel

299
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,880
a strong sense of trust.

300
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:19,000
So I told her

301
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,120
my story in detail.

302
00:16:20,560 --> 00:16:22,020
She said she could help me.

303
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,080
She could make Pei Xinlu

304
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:25,000
willingly kill Pei Xi.

305
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:26,680
She also said

306
00:16:27,480 --> 00:16:29,940
she could help me get revenge on Zhou Wanrou.

307
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,000
The condition is

308
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:34,130
to hand over Zhou Wanrou and Pei Xi to her after it's done.

309
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:35,700
As for what she plans to do,

310
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,060
she didn't say,

311
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,410
and I didn't ask.

312
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:43,200
You're willing to trust that fox,

313
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:45,120
who supposedly has the ability to make Pei Xinlu

314
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,920
willingly help you get revenge.

315
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,480
It's not just because of his guilt

316
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:50,940
for abandoning and betraying you back then.

317
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,200
Six months ago,

318
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:55,040
his company faced a financial crisis.

319
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:56,400
You happened to return to the country

320
00:16:56,400 --> 00:16:58,760
and helped him resolve those financial difficulties.

321
00:16:58,760 --> 00:16:59,920
So naturally,

322
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:01,520
you came back into his sight.

323
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,560
Because he needed your help.

324
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:06,280
So you shamelessly took control over him.

325
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,240
If I'm not mistaken,

326
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:10,780
Pei Xinlu's company's financial crisis

327
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:14,200
was also orchestrated by this fox you mentioned, right?

328
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:16,079
No matter how capable she is,

329
00:17:16,079 --> 00:17:18,119
she'll still treat you as a disposable pawn.

330
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:20,050
Even when you ran to Longyun Manor,

331
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:21,810
she still didn't let you go.

332
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:22,839
Tell me,

333
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:24,740
how did she find you there?

334
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,680
A week ago.

335
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:29,620
Pei Xinlu suddenly disappeared.

336
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:32,800
I was afraid he was taken away for questioning

337
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:34,680
because of Zhou Wanrou's death case.

338
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:36,280
So I changed my phone number.

339
00:17:37,560 --> 00:17:39,000
But I was still worried.

340
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,120
Longyun Villa

341
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:42,880
doesn't require real-name registration.

342
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:44,520
So I hid there.

343
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,410
I hesitated for a whole day.

344
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:49,530
I just sent the location to Fox.

345
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:52,810
Who knew I'd almost get myself killed.

346
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,540
Where is Zheng Lanshu?

347
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,120
Who took her there?

348
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,200
Is it this person?

349
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:03,520
It's her.

350
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:06,290
She's also the one who killed Zhou Wanrou.

351
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,520
I can't believe you've already found her.

352
00:18:09,520 --> 00:18:11,360
But you'll never find Fox.

353
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:13,370
What do you mean?

354
00:18:14,440 --> 00:18:15,520
Are you saying

355
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:18,250
this person is a scapegoat Fox prepared long ago?

356
00:18:20,040 --> 00:18:21,900
I should have realized it sooner.

357
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:24,280
At first, for some unknown reason,

358
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:26,000
Fox approached me.

359
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:29,170
Said she could help me get revenge.

360
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,880
The exchange was that

361
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,640
I had to hand Pei Xi over to her.

362
00:18:35,080 --> 00:18:36,680
But you didn't follow through,

363
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,200
so she abandoned you.

364
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:40,000
In the end, Zhou Wanrou died.

365
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:41,000
Zhou Wanrou's death

366
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,880
served the same purpose as Pei Xi would have.

367
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,880
Eventually she changed partners

368
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:46,800
to Zheng Lanshu.

369
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,560
She promised to help Zheng Lanshu get revenge

370
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:51,920
using the same method.

371
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,320
She killed the person responsible for

372
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:55,200
Pei Xi and Zhou Wanrou's deaths - Pei Xinlu.

373
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:56,040
And me too.

374
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:58,840
Finally, she planned to frame me

375
00:18:58,840 --> 00:19:00,300
for Zhou Wanrou's murder.

376
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:02,780
A perfect crime with no witness left.

377
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:11,360
The number twenty-five

378
00:19:11,520 --> 00:19:13,520
has appeared for the third time now.

379
00:19:13,840 --> 00:19:15,880
How did the evidence from the Zhou family massacre

380
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,340
end up in your possession?

381
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,760
Between these two cases,

382
00:19:18,760 --> 00:19:20,360
there must be some connection.

383
00:19:20,360 --> 00:19:22,880
We could have all escaped together.

384
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:24,920
Why did you do this?

385
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:27,240
Why?
